<p>My car has the same thing on the throttle and it’s not noticable with normal driving</p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":52,"updated_at":"2023-11-14T15:48:02.773Z","reply_count":2,"reply_to_post_number":4,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":294,"readers_count":293,"score":68.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":444269,"topic_slug":"swerve-control-a-bit-too-jumpy","display_username":"Technologyman00","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":60828,"username":"Dave1998","name":"","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/a88e57/{size}.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":25951,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":"7900, 1792, 1714"},"post_url":"/t/swerve-control-a-bit-too-jumpy/444269/5","custom_user_title":"7900, 1792, 1714","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3253381,"name":"","username":"Dave1998","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/a88e57/{size}.png","created_at":"2023-11-14T15:50:25.574Z","cooked":"<p>You can’t compare driving your car and driving an FRC robot… You need to give the driver the ability to make hard maneuvers to avoid collisions</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":52,"updated_at":"2023-11-14T15:50:25.574Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":5,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":290,"readers_count":289,"score":63.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":4442